metadata.name: Wild Maria {Full of Rage}
metadata.description:
"Wild Maria" is dedicated to the Divine Feminine mother goddess, shrouded in the fullness and depth of her blood mysteries, her wildness, and the unbridled rage of a thousand generations of women.

Featured Musician: Anna Diorio
Animated to an excerpt of "Wild Woman", from her album "Inner Grounds" (2018) produced by SriKala
